targets.queryText:
WITH RankedData AS (
    SELECT
        games.created_at AS 'time',
        10 - participants.op_score_rank AS 'Op Score',
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY games.created_at ASC) AS row_num
    FROM
        participants
    JOIN
        games ON participants.game_id = games.game_id
    JOIN
        champions ON participants.champion_id = champions.champion_id
    WHERE participants.summoner_name IN (${SUMMONER_NAME:singlequote})
),
MovingAverage AS (
    SELECT
        time,
        [Op Score],
        (SELECT AVG([Op Score])
         FROM RankedData r2
         WHERE r2.row_num BETWEEN r1.row_num - 5 AND r1.row_num + 5) AS Trendline
    FROM RankedData r1
)
SELECT
    time,
    [Op Score],
    Trendline
FROM MovingAverage
ORDER BY time ASC;

    games.created_at AS 'time',
    participants.team_key AS 'Side',
    10-participants.op_score_rank AS 'Score'
FROM
    participants
JOIN
    games ON participants.game_id = games.game_id
JOIN
        champions ON participants.champion_id = champions.champion_id
WHERE participants.summoner_name IN (${SUMMONER_NAME:singlequote})
    AND participants.team_key IN ('RED','BLUE')
ORDER BY 
    games.created_at ASC

FROM participants
GROUP BY participants.summoner_name
ORDER BY count(*) desc
LIMIT 1
